# 🚨 SOC Incident Playbook

## 1. Detection Example
sHIGH BRUTE FORCE: 9 SSH fails TOR IP 185.230.122.10 CRITICAL PII: SSN 123-45-6789 exposed in logs





## 2. Why It Matters
| Alert | Threat | Impact |
|-------|--------|--------|
| **Brute Force** | Attacker guessing passwords via TOR | Account compromise |
| **PII Exposure** | SSN/CC in logs | Identity theft, fines |

## 3. Triage & Response
BRUTE FORCE (9+ fails TOR):

grep "185.230.122.10" /var/log/auth.log
fail2ban-client set sshd banip 185.230.122.10
Alert: "IP blocked - monitor for lateral movement"
PII EXPOSURE (SSN/CC):

grep -r "123-45-6789" /var/log/
Rotate affected credentials
DLP scan: splunk search "SSN OR CC" | stats count




## 4. Escalation Matrix
< 5min: Analyst triage 5-30min: Senior SOC

30min: Incident Response

